==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lobster pot
<hw>Lob"ster pot</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a device used to
trap lobsters, consisting of a semi-cylindrical structure made of wooden
slats, with openings formed of funnel-shaped nets allowing lobsters to
enter, but impeding their exit. It is also called a <altname>lobster
trap</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lobsters thermidor</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Lobster thermidor</ent>⟦br⟧
